{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":440,"text":"The best Christmas my children ever had"},{"time":3600,"text":"was also the worst Christmas\nmy husband and I ever had."},{"time":7800,"text":"Elizabeth, age seven,"},{"time":9640,"text":"and her brother, Ian, age five,"},{"time":12520,"text":"couldn't imagine why they were getting\neverything they wanted for Christmas."},{"time":17240,"text":"The reason Santa was so generous"},{"time":20760,"text":"was because of something\nmy husband Pat and I knew"},{"time":24040,"text":"and the kids couldn't comprehend."},{"time":26440,"text":"Something that we had just learned,\nand it terrified us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31560,"text":"This was 1994"},{"time":33840,"text":"and the story actually starts\na few years earlier."},{"time":36800,"text":"For a couple of years I had noticed\na rash on the sides of Elizabeth's neck"},{"time":42400,"text":"that looked like prickly heat."},{"time":44960,"text":"For those same years,\nmy father and brother both died of cancer,"},{"time":49600,"text":"and I was probably\noveranxious about illness."},{"time":53120,"text":"The doctors assured us\nthere was nothing wrong"},{"time":55920,"text":"and I shouldn't worry,"},{"time":57680,"text":"but I wasn't so sure."},{"time":60200,"text":"And so without a referral,\nand paying out-of-pocket,"},{"time":63320,"text":"I took Elizabeth to a dermatologist."},{"time":66560,"text":"She was probably\njust allergic to something,"},{"time":68920,"text":"but why did it appear\njust on the sides of her neck, this rash?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":74840,"text":"So it's two days before Christmas,"},{"time":76800,"text":"1994,"},{"time":79200,"text":"and the dermatologist\ntakes a quick look at her neck and says,"},{"time":82600,"text":"\"She has pseudoxanthoma elasticum.\""},{"time":85640,"text":"And then he shuts off the lights\nand looks in her eyes."},{"time":90320,"text":"It turns out, by chance,"},{"time":92000,"text":"this dermatologist\nalso trained in ophthalmology."},{"time":96080,"text":"Our lucky day."},{"time":99400,"text":"I am sick to my stomach."},{"time":101640,"text":"\"Oma?\""},{"time":102920,"text":"Oma's like melanoma, lymphoma --"},{"time":105840,"text":"cancer."},{"time":107840,"text":"\"Why are you looking\nin her eyes for a skin rash?\""},{"time":111600,"text":"I scream and make no sound."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114720,"text":"So there it is."},{"time":116800,"text":"Elizabeth has pseudoxanthoma elasticum,"},{"time":121440,"text":"PXE for short."},{"time":124880,"text":"Questions mix with fear"},{"time":127200,"text":"and erupt like bile in my throat."},{"time":129919,"text":"Why are you looking in her eyes?"},{"time":132840,"text":"What do you know about this?\nHow do you know for sure?"},{"time":135840,"text":"What is the prognosis?"},{"time":138200,"text":"My training in pastoral counseling\ndid not prepare me for this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143680,"text":"Dr. Bercovitch tells us\neverything he knows about PXE."},{"time":148840,"text":"It's a rare genetic disorder,"},{"time":151800,"text":"it's systemic,"},{"time":154040,"text":"it's a slowly progressing,\npremature aging disease."},{"time":158840,"text":"It causes loose wrinkly skin\nin the flexor areas."},{"time":163600,"text":"It causes legal blindness,"},{"time":165560,"text":"like macular degeneration,"},{"time":167960,"text":"and a host of cardiovascular problems."},{"time":171680,"text":"Little is known about this disease,"},{"time":174600,"text":"and some people die in their 30s,"},{"time":177440,"text":"say some of the reports at the time."},{"time":181440,"text":"He then just glances at our son and says,"},{"time":186120,"text":"\"He has it, too.\""},{"time":189400,"text":"We want to flee\nback to the land of normal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198920,"text":"Two days after Christmas,"},{"time":200360,"text":"researchers come\nfrom a university in Boston,"},{"time":203400,"text":"and they take blood\nfrom us and our children"},{"time":205920,"text":"for a research project\nfocused on finding the gene."},{"time":209360,"text":"A few days later,"},{"time":210760,"text":"researchers come\nfrom a medical center in New York"},{"time":213200,"text":"and say they want blood, too."},{"time":215520,"text":"\"These are children."},{"time":217560,"text":"They're five and seven years old."},{"time":219680,"text":"Don't make them face the needle twice."},{"time":222360,"text":"Go and get your share\nfrom the other researchers.\""},{"time":226440,"text":"They laugh, incredulous."},{"time":228680,"text":"\"Share?\""},{"time":231200,"text":"It is then that we learn that there\nis little sharing in biomedical research."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236520,"text":"This moment, more than any other,"},{"time":239240,"text":"lit a fire beneath my husband Pat and me."},{"time":243640,"text":"Pat and I went to a medical school library"},{"time":245840,"text":"and we copied every article\nwe could find on PXE."},{"time":249720,"text":"We didn't understand a thing."},{"time":252840,"text":"We bought medical dictionaries\nand scientific textbooks"},{"time":255600,"text":"and read everything\nwe could get our hands on."},{"time":258560,"text":"And though we still didn't understand,"},{"time":260440,"text":"we could see patterns,"},{"time":262320,"text":"and it became quickly\napparent within a month"},{"time":265720,"text":"that there was no systematic effort\nto understand PXE."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"In addition,"},{"time":272240,"text":"the lack of sharing\nthat we experienced was pervasive."},{"time":276480,"text":"Researchers competed with each other"},{"time":279640,"text":"because the ecosystem\nwas designed to reward competition"},{"time":284560,"text":"rather than to alleviate suffering."},{"time":287840,"text":"We realized that we would have to do\nwork on this condition ourselves"},{"time":292880,"text":"to find solutions\nfor ourselves and others like us."},{"time":297560,"text":"But we faced two major barriers."},{"time":299920,"text":"The first one:"},{"time":301440,"text":"Pat and I have no science background."},{"time":304920,"text":"At the time, he's the manager\nof a construction company,"},{"time":308360,"text":"and I'm a former college chaplain\nstay-at-home mom --"},{"time":312240,"text":"hardly the backgrounds\nto take the research world by storm."},{"time":317480,"text":"The second barrier:"},{"time":320360,"text":"researchers don't share."},{"time":323000,"text":"People told us you can't herd cats."},{"time":326640,"text":"Well, yes you can if you move their food."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333400,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":337400,"text":"DNA and clinical data is the food."},{"time":340960,"text":"So we would collect blood\nand medical histories,"},{"time":344120,"text":"and require that all scientists\nusing these resources"},{"time":347720,"text":"would share results with each other\nand with the people who donated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353080,"text":"Well before the internet\nwas in common use,"},{"time":355320,"text":"Pat and I established PXE International,"},{"time":358200,"text":"a nonprofit dedicated to initiating\nresearch and conducting it on PXE"},{"time":363120,"text":"and also supporting\nindividuals with the disease."},{"time":367840,"text":"Using traditional media,"},{"time":369200,"text":"we garnered around\n100-150 people around the world"},{"time":373640,"text":"who we asked,"},{"time":374920,"text":"would you give us your blood,\nyour tissue, your medical histories,"},{"time":378200,"text":"your medical records?"},{"time":380200,"text":"And we brought all of that together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":382920,"text":"We quickly learned that this shared\nresource was not going to be enough."},{"time":387920,"text":"And so we decided we had\nto do hardcore bench science --"},{"time":393280,"text":"hardcore research."},{"time":395400,"text":"So we borrowed bench space\nat a lab at Harvard."},{"time":398200,"text":"A wonderful neighbor\ncame a couple times a week"},{"time":401000,"text":"and sat with the kids from 8pm to 2am"},{"time":405080,"text":"while Pat and I extracted DNA,"},{"time":407440,"text":"ran and scored gels"},{"time":409200,"text":"and searched for the gene."},{"time":411240,"text":"Generous postdocs\ntutored us as we went along."},{"time":414640,"text":"Within a few years, we found the gene."},{"time":417360,"text":"We patented it so that\nit would be freely available."},{"time":420400,"text":"We created a diagnostic test."},{"time":422480,"text":"We put together a research consortium."},{"time":425600,"text":"We held research meetings\nand opened a center of excellence."},{"time":429360,"text":"We found more than 4,000 people\naround the world who had PXE,"},{"time":434760,"text":"and held patient meetings"},{"time":436720,"text":"and did clinical trials and studies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440840,"text":"Through all this,"},{"time":442360,"text":"we lived with fear."},{"time":445040,"text":"Fear of the disease\nbreathing down our neck"},{"time":449360,"text":"while the clock ticked."},{"time":451280,"text":"Fear of researchers,"},{"time":454200,"text":"so well credentialed and positioned\nin a world made for them."},{"time":458920,"text":"Fear that we were making\nthe wrong choices."},{"time":462440,"text":"Fear that the naysayers were right"},{"time":464800,"text":"and the cats would simply find a new food."},{"time":468800,"text":"But greater than all these fears\nwas our drive to make a difference"},{"time":472000,"text":"for our kids and for all those\nwe had met along the way."},{"time":476280,"text":"And very quickly,"},{"time":477520,"text":"we also realized what we\nwere doing for one disease,"},{"time":480280,"text":"we should do for all diseases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484200,"text":"We joined with, and I eventually led,"},{"time":486040,"text":"Genetic Alliance --"},{"time":487280,"text":"a network of health advocacy,"},{"time":489600,"text":"patient advocacy,"},{"time":490840,"text":"research and health organizations."},{"time":493160,"text":"We built scalable\nand extensible resources,"},{"time":495640,"text":"like biobanks and registries\nand directories of support"},{"time":498480,"text":"for all diseases."},{"time":500800,"text":"And as I learned about all those diseases\nand all those disease communities,"},{"time":504880,"text":"I realized that there were\ntwo secrets in health care"},{"time":507760,"text":"that were impacting me greatly."},{"time":510480,"text":"The first:"},{"time":511760,"text":"there are no ready answers\nfor people like my kids"},{"time":515200,"text":"or all the people I was working with,"},{"time":517159,"text":"whether common or rare conditions."},{"time":519919,"text":"And the second secret:"},{"time":521760,"text":"the answers lie in all of us together,"},{"time":525880,"text":"donating our data,"},{"time":528240,"text":"our biological samples"},{"time":530560,"text":"and ultimately ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":534440,"text":"There is a small\ngroundswell of individuals"},{"time":537800,"text":"who are working to change this."},{"time":540080,"text":"Citizen scientists, activists, hacks"},{"time":543160,"text":"who are using crowdsourcing,\ndo-it-yourself science"},{"time":546360,"text":"are changing the game."},{"time":548600,"text":"Even President Obama\nand Vice President Biden"},{"time":552680,"text":"are evangelists for the idea"},{"time":554400,"text":"that people should be\npartners in research."},{"time":557680,"text":"This is a founding principle\nof our organization."},{"time":560960,"text":"Sure, it's really hard"},{"time":563120,"text":"to discover and develop\ninterventions and therapies."},{"time":567480,"text":"The science is hard,"},{"time":569840,"text":"the regulatory regime is difficult."},{"time":572960,"text":"There are a lot of stakeholders\nwith lots of interests"},{"time":576000,"text":"and misaligned incentives\nlike publishing, promotion and tenure."},{"time":581360,"text":"I don't fault scientists\nfor following this path,"},{"time":584800,"text":"but I challenge them and us\nto do this differently."},{"time":588400,"text":"To recognize that people\nare at the center."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593400,"text":"Genetic Alliance has experimented"},{"time":595200,"text":"in what it will take\nto transform these crusty systems."},{"time":600920,"text":"Our goal is to work without boundaries."},{"time":603880,"text":"That sounds abstract,\nbut for us it's quite practical."},{"time":609400,"text":"When we're frustrated\nthat entities won't share data --"},{"time":613120,"text":"data that comes from people who gave\ntheir energy, their time, their blood"},{"time":618240,"text":"and even their tears --"},{"time":620520,"text":"we need to stop and ask,"},{"time":622160,"text":"\"How is it true that we\ncould share, but we aren't?\""},{"time":625840,"text":"We're part of this system, too."},{"time":630440,"text":"How do we make it\nso that people can share ideas freely?"},{"time":635400,"text":"So that people can take risks\nand move closer to one another?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":641480,"text":"This leads to a dissolving\nof us versus them,"},{"time":644760,"text":"not only for organizations\nbut also for individuals."},{"time":648720,"text":"If I'm going to ask\norganizations or individuals"},{"time":652120,"text":"to strive for these standards,"},{"time":654360,"text":"then I too need to explore\nmy own being and my practices."},{"time":660120,"text":"If I'm going to ask clinicians\nand researchers and administrators"},{"time":663400,"text":"to take risks,"},{"time":665000,"text":"then I, Sharon,\nneed to take risks as well."},{"time":668840,"text":"I need to face my personal fears."},{"time":672680,"text":"My fear of not having enough impact."},{"time":677400,"text":"My fear of not leading well."},{"time":681000,"text":"My fear of not being enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686720,"text":"Just before they entered their teens,\nour kids stopped us in our tracks"},{"time":690680,"text":"and said, \"You have to stop worrying\nabout making a difference,"},{"time":694400,"text":"making an impact,"},{"time":695680,"text":"and instead, like us,\nlearn to live with disease"},{"time":699680,"text":"rather than fight it.\""},{"time":704600,"text":"I have to ask,"},{"time":705920,"text":"where does all my fear come from?"},{"time":709320,"text":"The kids' declaration\nshines a spotlight on that fear."},{"time":713760,"text":"It arises from a bedrock of love."},{"time":717920,"text":"I love Elizabeth and Ian."},{"time":722320,"text":"I love people with PXE."},{"time":725520,"text":"I love people with any disease."},{"time":728720,"text":"I love people."},{"time":732520,"text":"Some of my colleagues have discovered\nthat it is not death we fear,"},{"time":737160,"text":"it is the enormity of our loving."},{"time":740760,"text":"This expansive love opens me to great pain"},{"time":745560,"text":"as I face loss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749040,"text":"As I discover my fear,"},{"time":752160,"text":"I discover that I"},{"time":753960,"text":"and all those around me"},{"time":755600,"text":"have boundless capacity for love."},{"time":761640,"text":"And I also discover"},{"time":764240,"text":"as I move into this fear,"},{"time":767400,"text":"that I can learn many new things"},{"time":769880,"text":"and find paths"},{"time":772320,"text":"to things like practical solutions"},{"time":776200,"text":"as well as the core of healing and health."}]},{"cues":[{"time":783000,"text":"I don't fear fear the way I used to."},{"time":788560,"text":"In fact lately, with enormous support\nfrom all my fellow journeyers,"},{"time":793720,"text":"I notice that it's not a warning\nthe way it used to be."},{"time":798040,"text":"I notice that instead,"},{"time":800920,"text":"it's an invitation to go forward"},{"time":802840,"text":"because in it lies love\nand the path to greater love."},{"time":807640,"text":"If I turn with gentle curiosity\ntoward that fear,"},{"time":812800,"text":"I find enormous wealth\nwithin myself and others"},{"time":817880,"text":"and the ability to step into challenges\nthat I never thought I could."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822960,"text":"My kids are ahead of me\non that path still."},{"time":826360,"text":"At ages 29 and 27,"},{"time":828280,"text":"they declare they are happy and healthy"},{"time":830760,"text":"despite having manifestations of PXE\nin their skin and eyes and arteries."},{"time":837160,"text":"And so I invite you, us, we,"},{"time":840520,"text":"to turn toward our fear;"},{"time":842120,"text":"to embrace the things that scare us"},{"time":845080,"text":"and find the love at the center."},{"time":847240,"text":"We'll not only find ourselves there"},{"time":849480,"text":"but we'll also be able\nto step into the shoes of those we fear"},{"time":853480,"text":"and those who fear us."},{"time":855440,"text":"If we breathe into that fear"},{"time":858560,"text":"and are vulnerable with the systems\nand people who challenge us,"},{"time":863240,"text":"our power as changemakers\ngrows exponentially."},{"time":868400,"text":"And when we realize"},{"time":869680,"text":"that working on our inner life\nis working on our outer life"},{"time":873360,"text":"and outer work is inner work,"},{"time":876120,"text":"we get down to what is real"},{"time":878280,"text":"and shit gets done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":879720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":881200,"text":"There is no limit\nto what we can accomplish together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":885040,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":886280,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}